OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FProtesters have pelted police with
OL,7,Fmissiles in clashes close to where
OL,8,FHenry Nowak was stabbed to death.
OL,10,FHundreds gathered outside Southampton
OL,11,FCentral Police Station on Tuesday
OL,12,Fwhere activist Tommy Robinson and
OL,13,FLaurence Fox were among those who
OL,14,Fspoke to the crowd.
OL,16,FViolent scenes broke out after a large
OL,17,Fgroup walked across town to the area
OL,18,Fof Portswood.
OL,20,FA police helicopter hovered overhead
OL,21,Fas officers were pelted with stones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780448626
OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FDemonstrators chanted "Henry, Henry"
OL,7,Fas the line of police were pelted with
OL,8,Fbricks.
OL,10,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,11,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,12,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,13,Fback from the line they had been
OL,14,Fholding.
OL,16,FThe killer of finance student Mr
OL,17,FNowak, 23-year-old Vickrum Digwa, told
OL,18,Fpolice attending the scene of the
OL,19,Fstabbing in Southampton on December 3
OL,20,F2025 that he had been the victim of a
OL,21,Fracist attack.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
