OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780448626
OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FIn body-worn camera footage from the
OL,7,Fincident, Mr Nowak can be heard
OL,8,Frepeatedly saying: "I've been
OL,9,Fstabbed", to which an officer replies:
OL,10,F"Don't think you have, mate."
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood later
OL,13,Fcondemned the scenes in Portswood as
OL,14,F"completely unacceptable" and accused
OL,15,Fthe demonstrators of "hijacking this
OL,16,Ftragedy to stir up violence and
OL,17,Fdisorder" in defiance of a plea by the
OL,18,FNowak family not to use the murder to
OL,19,Ffeed division and hatred.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@HO]rD@AOUrD@]O]vD@AOUvD@YO]wD@
OL,26,AVOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
