OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780448626
OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe clashes with police come amid
OL,7,Fgrowing tensions and scrutiny over how
OL,8,Fofficers dealt with the incident which
OL,9,Fincluded arresting and handcuffing Mr
OL,10,FNowak as he lay dying.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood said: "The Nowak family
OL,13,Fmade a powerful call to us all
OL,14,Fyesterday to not let Henry's death be
OL,15,Fused to create further division,
OL,16,Fhatred or tension.
OL,26,@tD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780448626
OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"There can be no justification for
OL,7,Fhijacking this tragedy to stir up
OL,8,Fviolence and disorder. Those
OL,9,Fresponsible can expect to face the
OL,10,Ffull force of the law.
OL,12,F"I thank the police who have tonight
OL,13,Fshown great bravery and calm in the
OL,14,Fface of disgraceful violence directed
OL,15,Fat them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
