OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FEarlier on Tuesday Hampshire Police
OL,7,Fsaid an officer not connected to the
OL,8,Fcase has faced death threats after
OL,9,Fbeing misidentified in online posts.
OL,11,FIn a post on X, the force said: "We
OL,12,Frecognise the desire for answers about
OL,13,Fthe police response that night" and
OL,14,Fwarned people not to indulge in
OL,15,F"harmful online speculation".
OL,26,@sD@aOUuD@_O]wD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
