SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780448626
OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fsaid he "felt sick" watching
OL,8,F"harrowing" footage of police
OL,9,Fhandcuffing Mr Nowak and said there
OL,10,Fare "serious questions" to answer
OL,11,Fabout the case.
OL,13,FThere needs to be an examination into
OL,14,Fhow "accusations of racism" informed
OL,15,Fthe police's decision-making in the
OL,16,Fcase, he added.
OL,18,FThe police watchdog is expected to
OL,19,Freport on the case within the next
OL,20,Fthree months.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@SO]pD@AOUpD@KO]rD@EOUrD@WO]vD@
OL,26,AEOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
