PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780448626
OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FMr Nowak's father Mark Nowak, speaking
OL,7,Fafter Digwa was sentenced on Monday,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We do not want his death to be
OL,9,Fused to create further division,
OL,10,Fhatred or tension."
OL,12,FBut Reform UK leader Nigel Farage said
OL,13,Fpeople should respond with "pure cold
OL,14,Frage" to Mr Nowak's treatment, which
OL,15,Fhe said was evidence of a "two-tier
OL,16,Fculture".
OL,18,FMr Nowak was "actually treated in a
OL,19,Fway that meant an accusation of a
OL,20,Fracial slur was treated more seriously
OL,21,Fthan an act of murder", Mr Farage said.
OL,26,@pD@GOUrD@SO]uD@\OUvD@EO]wD@[OUxD@HO]zD@
OL,26,ANOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
