OL,3,CProtesters clash with police in
OL,4,CSouthampton over Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FIn other developments:
OL,8,F` Attorney General Lord Hermer has
OL,9,Freceived "multiple requests" to
OL,10,Fconsider whether Digwa's sentence
OL,11,Fshould be reviewed as unduly lenient.
OL,13,F` Digwa, his father Moga Singh, 52,
OL,14,Fand brother Gurpreet Digwa, 27,
OL,15,Fappeared at Southampton Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt to face multiple weapons charges.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
